SOCIAL INTERACTIONS

Noticed more collaborative work today than usual. Maybe because culture materials lend themselves to sharing?

Emma and Zoe worked together on animal cards - taking turns, discussing answers.

Oscar asked Lucas for help finding Asia on the puzzle map.

No major conflicts during this observation period. Group dynamic seems good right now.

